    "faqFree": "Is LumiAI free to use?",
    "faqFreeAnswer": "Yes! LumiAI has a free tier that includes basic access to AI tools, marketplace browsing, and analytics. Premium features like advanced AI generation and contract scanning require a subscription.",
    "faqDemo": "How do demo accounts work?",
    "faqDemoAnswer": "We provide demo accounts so you can explore all features. Use sarah@demo.com (creator), glow@demo.com (company), or admin@lumiai.com (admin) with password 'demo123' (or 'admin123' for admin).",
    "faqInsurance": "How does equipment rental insurance work?",
    "faqInsuranceAnswer": "Basic insurance is included with every rental. It covers normal wear and tear. Full coverage is available as an add-on for expensive items. Deposits are held on your card and released after return inspection.",
    "faqNegotiate": "Can I negotiate rates with brands?",
    "faqNegotiateAnswer": "Absolutely! Our marketplace shows suggested rate ranges, but you can always propose your own rates. Use our Market Advisor tool to understand what you should be charging based on your metrics.",
    "faqSecure": "Is my contract data secure when using the scanner?",
    "faqSecureAnswer": "Yes. Contract data is processed securely and never stored on our servers. We recommend removing personal information before uploading for extra safety.",
